s act exactly as a mirror does when turned off, meaning <strong>you can see your reflection <\/strong>and use it just as you would any other mirror!<br\/><br\/>However, when it's switched on it opens up an <strong>infinite portal into another dimension <\/strong>through all the breathtaking colors and effects.<\/p>"}},"question_WnYGi9":{"type":"question","settings":{"question":"Do you offer Warranty on the Infinity Mirrors?","answer":"<p>We are more than pleased to offer our customers a <strong>2 year warranty <\/strong>on the Infinity Mirror. Our Casa Guarantee entitles you to a full replacement or refund of the product.<\/p>"}},"question_VgbTp9":{"type":"question","settings":{"question":"How long will my Infinity Mirror last?","answer":"<p>Efficient use of modern LEDs can ensure a <strong>lifetime of functionality<\/strong>. When operated 24\/7, they're designed to last <strong>at least 10 years<\/strong>.<\/p>"}},"question_PXENUE":{"type":"question","settings":{"question":"Is the Infinity Mirror worldwide compatible?","answer":"<p>Our Infinity Mirrors are <strong>worldwide compatible <\/strong>and will work for any power voltage (100V-240V).<br\/><br\/>Your Infinity Mirror package will include a power plug with attachments for US, AU, UK and EU socket compatibility.<br\/><\/p>"}}},"block_order":["category_MMzhzT","question_mxxNJT","question_FNAGp7","question_WnYGi9","question_VgbTp9","question_PXENUE"],"name":"FAQ Page v2","settings":{"auto_hide":true,"layout_style":"tabs-top","content_align":"left","title":"Frequently Asked Questions","subtitle":"Everything you need to know about our premium lighting collection","badge_text":"Support","show_search":false,"contact_title":"Still have questions?","contact_text":"Our team is here to help you find the perfect lighting solution.","contact_email":"","contact_page_url":"shopify:\/\/pages\/contact-us","contact_page_label":"Contact Us","color_bg":"#050505","color_text":"#f5f5f5","color_muted":"#a3a3a3","color_accent_prima